{"image_id": "EXPE_2009_page_93", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Expedia, Inc.", "bbox": [560.2, 140.2, 677.8, 161.0]}, {"text": "Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements — (Continued)", "bbox": [355.9, 177.7, 882.0, 198.5]}, {"text": "consider such other quantitative and qualitative factors we consider relevant, which may change depending on", "bbox": [143.8, 227.9, 1064.0, 248.8]}, {"text": "the date for which the assessment is made. This assessment resulted in the recognition in the fourth quarter of", "bbox": [143.8, 252.9, 1058.5, 273.8]}, {"text": "2008 of a loss on impairment of long-term assets of approximately $3 billion, which consists of $2.8 billion of", "bbox": [143.8, 277.9, 1066.0, 298.8]}, {"text": "goodwill and $223 million of indefinite-lived trade names. A deferred tax benefit of $189 million was recognized", "bbox": [143.8, 302.9, 1091.8, 323.8]}, {"text": "as a result of these charges. Of the $2.8 billion goodwill impairment charge in 2008, $2.0 billion related to our", "bbox": [143.8, 328.0, 1065.3, 348.8]}, {"text": "North America segment, $759 million to our Europe segment and $21 million in our Asia Pacific segment based", "bbox": [143.8, 353.0, 1083.1, 373.8]}, {"text": "on our segments for the year ended December 31, 2008. Based on our new segments for 2009, $2.5 billion of the", "bbox": [143.8, 378.0, 1086.1, 398.8]}, {"text": "goodwill impairment would have related to our Leisure segment and $282 million to our TripAdvisor Media", "bbox": [143.8, 403.0, 1050.0, 423.8]}, {"text": "Network segment. Of the $223 million indefinite-lived trade name impairment charge in 2008, $128 million", "bbox": [143.8, 428.0, 1047.2, 448.8]}, {"text": "related to trade names in our North America segment, $73 million in our Europe segment and $22 million in our", "bbox": [143.8, 453.0, 1082.1, 473.8]}, {"text": "Asia Pacific segment based on our segments for the year ended December 31, 2008. Based on our new segments", "bbox": [143.8, 478.0, 1083.7, 498.8]}, {"text": "for 2009, all such impairments would have related to our Leisure segment.", "bbox": [143.8, 503.0, 765.9, 523.8]}, {"text": "We determined that the adverse change in the business climate discussed above was also an indicator", "bbox": [185.5, 539.3, 1030.2, 560.1]}, {"text": "requiring the testing of our long-lived assets for recoverability and performed this test as of December 1, 2008.", "bbox": [143.8, 564.3, 1070.1, 585.1]}, {"text": "We tested the long-lived assets of our reporting units for recoverability based on a comparison of the respective", "bbox": [143.8, 589.3, 1075.7, 610.1]}, {"text": "aggregate values of their undiscounted cash flows to the respective carrying values. The results of the evaluation", "bbox": [143.8, 614.3, 1083.7, 635.1]}, {"text": "indicated that the carrying values of the related assets were recoverable. In addition to the above impairment", "bbox": [143.8, 639.3, 1049.0, 660.1]}, {"text": "analysis, during the fourth quarter of 2008, we wrote off $11 million related to capitalized software costs based", "bbox": [143.8, 664.3, 1072.2, 685.1]}, {"text": "on the abandonment of the related project.", "bbox": [143.8, 689.3, 496.8, 710.2]}, {"text": "Goodwill.", "bbox": [185.5, 725.4, 268.3, 746.2]}, {"text": "The following table presents the changes in goodwill by reportable segment:", "bbox": [289.2, 725.6, 928.0, 746.4]}, {"text": "Leisure", "bbox": [611.8, 773.2, 665.5, 789.9]}, {"text": "TripAdvisor", "bbox": [728.2, 756.5, 817.1, 773.2]}, {"text": "Media Network", "bbox": [716.9, 773.2, 828.4, 789.9]}, {"text": "Egencia", "bbox": [865.3, 773.2, 921.9, 789.9]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [986.6, 773.2, 1024.6, 789.9]}, {"text": "(In thousands)", "bbox": [770.5, 798.2, 873.8, 814.9]}, {"text": "Balance as of January 1, 2009 . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [185.5, 820.2, 560.5, 841.0]}, {"text": "$2,790,678", "bbox": [591.8, 820.2, 685.6, 841.0]}, {"text": "$704,749", "bbox": [733.6, 820.2, 811.8, 841.0]},